Class Medium

  • java.lang.Object
    • Medium

  • public class Medium
extends java.lang.Object
    Medium manages most of the graphics you see during games, such as clouds, ground, and dust. This class was edited and re-edited again by Chaotic for (mostly) full NFMM Graphics (excluding sparks and extra dust).
    Author:
    Kaffeinated, Chaotic, Omar Wally
